{"tid":1174014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟連登仔圍完爐未","createTime":"2019-05-27T13:43:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T13:57:16.000Z","uid":247897,"like":2,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"af218814de6d6eb10b692cf019db2818a9fcfb95","tid":1174014,"uid":247897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:43:55.000Z","msg":"日日夜夜係到叫6月9，話外國關注，話取消關係法。事實就只不過係自己圍爐取暖。唔好再同我講話咩出嚟可能失敗，但唔試過一定唔得之類嘅廢話。問下你自己，你真係覺得好多香港人反對，定係嗰啲只不過係你啲friend 同連登仔？你地成日覺得外國會介入，你地睇下緬甸死幾多人有冇介入？唔好人地一兩個聲明就打曬飛機啦。<br />\n<br />\n我唔係最窮個班人話自己冇嘢輸，但我都冇資格移民，都係要留喺到。我真心覺得啲師奶廢老公務員有錢佬係咁on9，我都唔介意送佢地一程。攬炒我都會輸，但我輸得起，而且仲會好開心。<br />\n<br />\n雖然我話我食催淚彈你地都會話我係三毛，但我都利申左先。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af71f30559ffe7e875a03aa7cbadbf336724b4b8","tid":1174014,"uid":25240,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:45:07.000Z","msg":"信你<br />\n#247897<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"960c42a5d8d9c106eb98e63ab3b1e8212bda3828","tid":1174014,"uid":247897,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"af71f30559ffe7e875a03aa7cbadbf336724b4b8","tid":1174014,"uid":25240,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:45:07.000Z","msg":"信你<br />\n#247897<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:46:55.000Z","msg":"隨便<br />\n會員號碼代表一切<br />\n廢老邏輯"},{"pid":"8b6a03eced1d65d660295ee7264773745b8a2b7d","tid":1174014,"uid":35014,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:46:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b0b0d9351d7936036eba485277ef8987f873f0f","tid":1174014,"uid":27452,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:48:31.000Z","msg":"不如我比夠$3你呀<br />\n你停啦好冇<br />\n何必貪個三毫子呢"},{"pid":"ca1e22040c2f4d93d62323a6f8b446efe4fc5a3c","tid":1174014,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:49:24.000Z","msg":"買定花生睇好戲"},{"pid":"3d46